casebody.data:
No. 640,

Misc.

Daugherty v. Ellis, Corrections Director. Petitioner pro se. Will Wilson, Attorney General of Texas, and Sam R. Wilson, Leon F. Pesek and Charles R. Lind, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Motion to substitute Jack Heard in the place of O. B. Ellis as the party respondent granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Texas denied.
